{
  "schema": 1,
  "id": "angel_light",
  "name": {
    "en": "Angel Light",
    "zh": "天使光"
  },
  "desc": {
    "en": "A large glowing panel presses down from above, with a bounce board below returning light to the face. Clean skin, soft shadow edges.",
    "zh": "頭頂一塊很大的發光物體壓下來，下方擺一塊反光板把光補回臉。皮膚乾淨、陰影邊際柔和。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "The floor colour changes how much of the top light bounces back onto the character. A brighter floor bounces more, a darker one absorbs more.",
    "zh": "透過底部的地板顏色，可以改變頂部光源透過地板反射到角色身上的效果，地板顏色越亮，反光越強，反之越深則越吃光。"
  },
  "engine_note": null,
